        {/* Gameplay Tips */}
        <section className="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-800/50 to-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-700/50">
          <h2 className="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span className="text-yellow-400">💡</span>
            Pro Tips & Strategies
          </h2>
          
          <div className="space-y-4">
            <div className="bg-yellow-900/20 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4 rounded-r-xl">
              <h3 className="font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-2">🎯 Team Composition Matters</h3>
              <p className="text-gray-300">
                Balance your team with different roles: a tank (like All Might), a damage dealer (like Bakugo), and support (like Uraraka). Synergize Quirks for devastating combo attacks.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div className="bg-blue-900/20 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 rounded-r-xl">
              <h3 className="font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">⚡ Master Character Switching</h3>
              <p className="text-gray-300">
                Don't just stick to one character. Switch mid-combo to extend combos, save low-health teammates, or counter specific enemy Quirks. Tag mechanics are crucial for high-level play.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div className="bg-green-900/20 border-l-4 border-green-500 p-4 rounded-r-xl">
              <h3 className="font-bold text-green-400 mb-2">🛡️ Defense is Key</h3>
              <p className="text-gray-300">
                Learn to block, dodge, and counter. Each character has unique defensive options. Mastering guard breaks and counter attacks will give you a huge advantage in competitive matches.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div className="bg-purple-900/20 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-4 rounded-r-xl">
              <h3 className="font-bold text-purple-400 mb-2">💥 Ultimate Timing</h3>
              <p className="text-gray-300">
                Don't waste your ultimate attacks! Save them for critical moments, combo extensions, or to punish whiffed enemy attacks. Team ultimates deal massive damage when coordinated properly.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div className="bg-red-900/20 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-4 rounded-r-xl">
              <h3 className="font-bold text-red-400 mb-2">🎓 Use Training Mode</h3>
              <p className="text-gray-300">
                Spend time in Training Mode to learn each character's move properties, combo routes, and Quirk interactions. Knowledge is power in competitive fighting games!
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

